#<Case>

# MWG: removed original orthography line, since it's only for the first example
# അവന്‍ഉനനൌന്നു
#* noun-nom intrans-verb
Source: {a:107}
Vetted: {s}
Judgment: {g}
Phenomena: {case}
avan unanaunnu
avan unanaunnu
he eat-PRES   
he is having his meal
  
#* *noun-acc intrans-verb
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
avane unanaunnu
avan-e unanaunnu
he-ACC eat-PRES   
he is having his meal
  
#* *noun-dat intrans-verb
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
avannə unanaunnu
avan-nə unanaunnu
he-DAT eat-PRES   
he is having his meal
  

#* noun-nom noun-acc trans-verb 
Source: {a:193}
Vetted: {s}
Judgment: {g}
Phenomena: {case}
kutatai ammaye     vilaiccu
kutatai amma-ye    vilaicc-u
child   mother-ACC call-PAST
the child called the mother

#* *noun-acc noun-acc trans-verb
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
kutataiye ammaye     vilaiccu
kutatai-ye amma-ye    vilaicc-u
child-ACC   mother-ACC call-PAST
the child called the mother

#* *noun-dat noun-acc trans-verb 
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
kutataikkə ammaye     vilaiccu
kutatai-kkə amma-ye    vilaicc-u
child-DAT   mother-ACC call-PAST
the child called the mother

#* *noun-nom noun-nom trans-verb 
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
kutatai amma     vilaiccu
kutatai amma    vilaicc-u
child-NOM   mother-NOM call-PAST
the child called the mother

#* *noun-nom noun-dat trans-verb 
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
kutatai ammakkə     vilaiccu
kutatai amma-kkə    vilaicc-u
child-NOM   mother-DAT call-PAST
the child called the mother

#* noun-dat noun-nom noun-nom ditrans-verb
Source: {a:193}
Vetted: {s}
Judgment: {g}
Phenomena: {case}
kutataikkə amma     paal kotautatau
kutatai-kkə amma     paal kotautatau
child-DAT  mother   milk gave-PAST
the mother gave the child milk

#* *noun-nom noun-nom noun-nom ditrans-verb
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
kutatai amma     paal kotautatau
kutatai amma     paal kotautatau
child  mother   milk gave-PAST
the mother gave the child milk

#* *noun-acc noun-nom noun-nom ditrans-verb
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
kutataiye amma     paal kotautatau
kutatai-ye amma     paal kotautatau
child-ACC  mother   milk gave-PAST
the mother gave the child milk

#* *noun-acc noun-acc noun-nom ditrans-verb
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
kutatai amma     paal kotautatau
kutatai-ye amma-ye     paal kotautatau
child-ACC  mother-ACC   milk gave-PAST
the mother gave the child milk

#* *noun-dat noun-dat noun-nom ditrans-verb
Source: {WBannister}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: {u}
Phenomena: {case}
kutataikkə ammakkə     paal kotautatau
kutatai-kkə amma-kkə     paal kotautatau
